<br>
I know I'm ASSuming here, but before the patch were you using your highest level pet? The one that had more ATK and hit for more than the not-highest-level pets? <br>
<br>
If you were killing at the same rate you were before, and your pet wasn't hitting for max, what do you think the reason is?<br>
<br>
More ATK = more damage = faster killing.<br>
<br>
But! Lesser level = less damage = slower killing.<br>
<br>
Apparently the two could cancel each other out fairly well.<br>
<br>
